description:
Quiet 1 bedroom apartment located in luxury complex. Queen size bed and couch for any additional guests. 2 Minute walk to J & M subway line. 1 minute walk to broadway featuring restraunts , cafes, shopping, grocery stores, banks, & Bus lines.

Parking on Street
Elevator in Building

Safe & secure building. Individual lock and key on bedroom door for extra security. 

My place is good for artists, adventurers, vacationers, and business travelers.
house_rules:
• Check in is anytime after 3PM
• No parties or events
• Not suitable for pets
• No smoking
name: Cozy Apartment off J&M Subway Lines

photos.caption: Kitchen fully equipped with stainless steel appliances, pots & pans, dishes, silverware, dishwasher, coffee pot, etc.
Spacious bedroom with queen size bed & with large picture window overlooking park
Individual Heating, Air conditioning & Fan control (wall mount) in each room
Don't forget to say hello to Michael the fish!
Large Shower/tub with rain shower head and water filter that removes any smells or chlorines
Lets not forget about the most amazing rooftop view looking at lower manhattan!
Flushing Avenue J&M Subway Station a 2 minute walk
Flush Avenue Subway Station from the Platform
Located around the corner on Broadway - Shopping, Restaraunts, Cafes, Banks, Planet Fitness, Wallgreens and the B46, B47 & B54  Buses
